---
// 文末 CTA：把变现入口串起来（newsletter + services + sponsorship）
---

<section class="cta">
  <div class="cta-h">// next.txt ›</div>

  <div class="cta-grid">
    <a class="cta-card" href="/newsletter">
      <div class="cta-card-h">📬 Subscribe</div>
      <div class="cta-card-t">Frontier Brief</div>
      <div class="cta-card-d">One signal per week. No AI filler.</div>
    </a>

    <a class="cta-card" href="/services">
      <div class="cta-card-h">🛠️ Work With Me</div>
      <div class="cta-card-t">AI engineering, hands-on</div>
      <div class="cta-card-d">Architecture review, RAG audit, build sprints.</div>
    </a>

    <a class="cta-card" href="/sponsorship">
      <div class="cta-card-h">💼 Sponsor</div>
      <div class="cta-card-t">Reach senior AI engineers</div>
      <div class="cta-card-d">Newsletter slots, sponsored deep-dives.</div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="disclosure">
    Some outbound links in this post are affiliate links — see <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">disclosure</a>.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    margin: 48px 0 32px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }
  .cta-h {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .cta-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .cta-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 14px 14px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent-green) 2%, transparent);
  }
  .cta-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-green);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .cta-card-h {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .cta-card-t {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 3px;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .cta-card-d {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .disclosure {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-text-faint);
    margin: 16px 0 0;
  }
  .disclosure a { color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
  .disclosure a:hover { color: var(--color-accent-green); }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .cta-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
